*event_6
;[exp] onObjectTrigger

@roadguide e="Swamp Ruins"

[eventoff]
;-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
*event_7
;[exp] WAY == "e"

@delevent
@wait time=500
[texton]
The bridge has collapsed.[k]
To proceed westward from here, we have no choice but to find some way to cross the swamp.[k]
[textoff]

[eventoff]
